high_descs: walk to the kitchen and go to the countertop.
take the butterknife off of the cutting board.
turn and walk to the eggplant in the living room.
Use the knife to cut the eggplant on the table.
turn around and walk to the front of the coffeetable.
Put down the butterknife on the coffeetable.
go back to the back of the eggplant.
pick up the eggplant from the table.
Take the eggplant to the kitchen sink.
Put the eggplant in the sink, turn the water on and then remove the eggplant.
walk to the front of the coffeetable and stand in front of the coffeetable.
Put down the eggplant on the coffeetable.
anns.task_desc: Gather all the eggplants and put them on the coffee table.

high_descs: Turn right, exit the room and then turn right to go to the cutting board on the countertop.
Pick up the butterknife from the cutting board.
Turn around and go to the eggplant table in front of the chair.
Slice the eggplant on the table.
Go around to the other side of the coffeetable.
Place the butterknife on the coffeetable.
Go around to the other side of the eggplant.
Pick up a slice of eggplant.
Turn left and go to the sink.
Place the slice of eggplant in the sink, rinse the eggplant with water and then pick up the eggplant slice.
Turn around and go back to the coffeetable with the knife.
Place the eggplant slice on the coffeetable.
anns.task_desc: Place a clean Eggplant slice on the CoffeeTable.

high_descs: Go to the door, turn left toward the countertop.
Pick up the butterknife on the cutting board.
Turn right and go across the room to the eggplant table in front of the sofa.
Slice the eggplant on the coffee table.
Turn around to the front of the coffeetable closer to the TV.
Put the butterknife on the coffeetable in the right corner closer to arm chair.
Go around to the side of the eggplant closer to the arm chair.
Pick up half of the eggplant closer to you.
Turn left, go across to the sink beside the fridge.
Place the eggplant in the sink, rinse the eggplant off, and pick the eggplant back up.
Head back to the coffeetable, go to the side closer to the TV.
Place the eggplant on the coffeetable in front of the knife, closer to the arm chair.
anns.task_desc: Put half of a cleaned Eggplant on the CoffeeTable.
